{"tid":947191,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"診所啱啱有條廢中好有自信磅重...","createTime":"2018-12-19T05:49:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T11:24:27.000Z","uid":164163,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ee22d4d2fd46cbf9faa38f44b384646589b9611b","tid":947191,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:49:24.000Z","msg":"話說今日小弟唔舒服 所以無返學 <br />\n走咗去睇醫生 咁診所入面都有幾個人等睇醫生 有兩母女(阿媽問佢十句嘢 個女(<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )就十問九唔應) 有一對老夫妻 同埋一個廢中<br />\n<br />\n個廢中一嚟到就已經小丸子咁Beli Bala Beli Bala 吵住啲護士姐姐(<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) 又話自己而家輕咗好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不斷咁同啲護士r水吹 過咗陣見到人哋無show佢 佢就面矇矇咁坐喺度等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後 突然間 佢同啲護士講佢想磅重 咁有個護士就出嚟幫佢磅 磅之前仲話自己應該都輕咗廿磅 應該160幾磅到 點知一磅 個磅針指向84kg 換言之 即係180幾磅 佢就即刻發哂爛渣 dum哂地咁離開間診所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正當大家以為佢真係走咗之後 可以排少一個 10分鐘後 佢返番嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不斷屌診所個磅唔準 佢自己啱啱返屋企磅完一次體重 話肯定無咁x重....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家話條廢中其實想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"df28a874a503245a6bc4f2610f7cfe9556b97d98","tid":947191,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:51:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c1fe0eb22ed5f0d1452aab34ee70989df812e120","tid":947191,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"df28a874a503245a6bc4f2610f7cfe9556b97d98","tid":947191,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:51:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:53:30.000Z","msg":"邊會有 佢坐喺我隔離 